      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like everything i touch breaks. i look at my kids and i just feel this massive weight of guilt cuz i know i'm not the parent they deserve. it feels like i'm just a shadow hanging over them, constantly dragging them down with my own mess. they'd be so much lighter without me constantly failing them.",
